comments: Would make a good stunt double for Wally Buono. He would also make a great hypnotist. I\'ve never known someone who can use the same jargon word three times in the same sentence, but he sure can. Loves to teach old outdated methods that won\'t help you whatsoever in the real world. Completely turned me off of surveying!

comments: He could be a salesman for HP inc. All he can talk about is his HP 50g calculator that does everything for him. But when you ask him a question, he asks you if you have a HP calculator, and no matter what you answer, you will tell you how to do it on a calculator.
